explanations.description: In the given text examples, the activated tokens are often part of scientific, technical, or medical terminology, particularly in fields such as parasitology, microbiology, and medicine. The activated tokens often appear to be suffixes or prefixes of words related to these fields, such as "asis", "osis", "ites", and "oma", or be part of a species name.
